title: Bach Collegium Japan - Handel's Messiah
description:
Bach Collegium of Japan performing Handel&#039;s Messiah.

It&#039;s a really solid recording, but I&#039;m quite certain they did a lot of digital editing because the runs are frighteningly clean and in time... see for yourself.
